      <section name='balloon'>

         <para number='1' comment='get balloon/round b/animal'>
         You cannot just take one of the balloons, you have to buy it!
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='pop/burst balloon'>
         The balloon droid moves away slightly, stopping you from bursting any of its balloons. It gives you a dirty look at gestures towards the price list on its torso.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='buy balloon'>
         You need to specify what kind of balloon you want - a round one or an animal one?
         </para>

         <para number='4' comment='rub any created balloons - play'>
         You rub the balloon, making an irritating squeaking noise. The resulting static electricity makes your hair stand on end.
         </para>

         <para number='5' comment='roomex'>
         A sudden irritating squeaking noise assails your ears. You look around and see that %s's hair is standing on end - it must be the static electricity from rubbing a balloon.
         </para>

         <para number='6' comment='drop - player'>
         You let go of the string and the balloon floats up out of reach, then vanishes into the distance.
         </para>

         <para number='7' comment='roomex'>
         A balloon floats upwards, released by %s, then vanishes into the distance.
         </para>

         <para number='8' comment='pop/burst - player'>
         You deliberately pop the balloon. It bursts with an ear-splittingly loud BANG, leaving just a few scraps of foil and a piece of string, which you discard.
         </para>

         <para number='9' comment='roomex'>
         You hear an ear-splittingly loud BANG - %s has just burst a balloon.
         </para>

