      <section name='balloondroid'>

         <para number='1' comment='Description'>
         The small droid is festooned with balloons of all different shapes and sizes, so many that it can barely keep its metal feet from being lifted off the ground. A sign hung around its neck gives the price list:
         </para>

         <para number='2'>
         It says that simple round colored balloons cost 2 groats. Buy one with BUY ROUND BALLOON.
         </para>

         <para number='3'>
         Balloons in the shape of animals cost 4 groats. Buy one with BUY ANIMAL BALLOON.
         </para>

      </section>

